divs: Sighting DetailsI was in the middle of my street about 8;30pm.when I saw two lights comeing from the eastern sky.I thought they were helichopters.They werent.As the lites approched,I heard two neighbors walking up the street behind me.It was a neighbor girl and her girlfreind,going too babysit at the corner house.I only looked at them for a second and looked back too the lites which were now a half mile away or closer REAL BIG LITES green or white.EST BIG as ahouse.one football feild apart. They seemed to turn south,then turned into two rows of 6or8 multicolored lites changeing colors.BIG ...then disappeared. The girls and I talked,did you see that??? I thought I was haveing stroke or something,But one girl said it didnt make a sound,Then off to our south we spotted a small plane and could hear it,we said they had to see it too.THATS IT Ill never get it out of my head .I draw it all the time....ANYBODY ELES REPORT THIS??????
